{"word":"H1086 - בָּלָה - bâlâh - baw-law' - Consume","slug":"H1086","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bâlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>baw-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consume"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - ba&#x0302;la&#x0302;h</b> - <i>baw-law'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>fail</i>; by implication to <i>wear out</i>, <i>decay</i> (causatively <i>consume</i>, <i>spend</i>): - consume, enjoy long, become (make, wax) old, spend, waste."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1077\">H1077</a>, <a href=\"#/H1087\">H1087</a>, <a href=\"#/H1094\">H1094</a>, <a href=\"#/H1097\">H1097</a>, <a href=\"#/H1099\">H1099</a>, <a href=\"#/H1100\">H1100</a>, <a href=\"#/H1107\">H1107</a>, <a href=\"#/H1115\">H1115</a>, <a href=\"#/H8399\">H8399</a>"}]}